Title: Delves: Breaking Tough to Loot Stuff
Description:
I've been itchin', $n. 

Itchin' to teach the delve critters a lesson! We need tae hit them hard. Hit the tough ones, so the weak ones will nae even poke their heads out!

Will ye join me?
ObjectivesText: Complete two Delves of Tier 6 or above.

Objectives.Text: Complete a delve at Tier 6 or above
